"{\"uid\": \"pressreleases.responsesource.com-news-105624-british-olympic-fencing-supplier-leon-paul-transforms-warehousing-and-drives\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"London, UK, 26 July 2024 -Leon Paul, the world's premier fencing equipment manufacturer, has transformed its warehousing and logistic operations and driven significant growth following its adoption of Forterro's ERP and Warehouse Management Solution,Orderwise.The 100-year-old family-run business produces and distributes 90% of its products from its London manufacturing and warehousing facility and had previously relied on a paper-based system.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999989204298, \"rank\": 1.0558691865211944e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 212, \"end\": 215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enterprise_resource_planning\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.502685017658743e-24, \"text\": \"ERP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enterprise_resource_planning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enterprise_resource_planning\"}, {\"begin\": 351, \"end\": 357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999958496004819, \"rank\": 3.6253054316658464e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's premier fencing equipment manufacturer\", \"from\": 37, \"to\": 87}, {\"ngram\": \"its warehousing and logistic operations\", \"from\": 105, \"to\": 144}, {\"ngram\": \"significant growth\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 174}, {\"ngram\": \"its adoption\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 197}, {\"ngram\": \"Orderwise\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 259}, {\"ngram\": \"The 100-year-old family-run business\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 296}, {\"ngram\": \"90%\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"its products\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 341}, {\"ngram\": \"warehousing facility\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 396}, {\"ngram\": \"a paper-based system\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was highly inefficient and resulted in a warehouse environment best described as 'chaos' and an estimated \\u00a3150,000 wastage every year in lost time and products, according to James Fay, Commercial Director, Leon Paul:\\\"We had no control of ordering from stock to delivery, no barcoding technology in the warehouse, no form of KPIs to manage our performance.\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_H._Fay\", \"score\": 0.9999999998399289, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Fay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_H._Fay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_H._Fay\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a warehouse environment\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"chaos\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 540}, {\"ngram\": \"an estimated \\u00a3150,000 wastage\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"lost time\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 599}, {\"ngram\": \"products\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 612}, {\"ngram\": \"Commercial Director\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 657}, {\"ngram\": \"Leon Paul:\\\"We\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"no control\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"stock\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"delivery\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 722}, {\"ngram\": \"no barcoding technology\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"the warehouse\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"no form\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"KPIs\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 781}, {\"ngram\": \"our performance\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We could not vet orders properly and were not even sure if products were being sent to the right places,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"orders\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 832}, {\"ngram\": \"products\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"the right places\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Morale was low amongst staff because they felt they could not do their jobs to the best of their ability, and we were wasting money, time and products hand over fist.\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Morale\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 931}, {\"ngram\": \"staff\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"their jobs\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"their ability\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"products\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"fist\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We were known for the quality of our fencing equipment, but our warehousing was far from Olympic standard.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1198, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the quality\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1121}, {\"ngram\": \"our fencing equipment\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"our warehousing\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic standard\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Orderwise was cost-effective and scalable, and it was actually recommended to me by a competitor, so it felt like the best fit for us right from the off.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Orderwise\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1208}, {\"ngram\": \"a competitor\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"the best fit\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Since implementing Orderwise, Leon Paul has been able to automate many processes and see vast efficiency improvements.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Orderwise\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"Leon Paul\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"many processes\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"vast efficiency improvements\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has eased pressure on employees, improved order management and customer service, and delivered a ten-fold increase in order processing.\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"employees\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1506}, {\"ngram\": \"improved order management\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"customer service\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"a ten-fold increase\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"order processing\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Order shipping time went from an average of nine days to less than one day.In a complex manufacturing environment-Leon Paul makes more than 3,000 SKUs, which can then become any one of 98,000 SKUs-Orderwise has become integral.\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Order shipping time\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1630}, {\"ngram\": \"an average\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"nine days\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1664}, {\"ngram\": \"less than one day\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"a complex manufacturing environment\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"Leon Paul\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1734}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 3,000 SKUs\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1761}, {\"ngram\": \"98,000 SKUs\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1807}, {\"ngram\": \"Orderwise\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It allows the business to make quick and informed decisions, and it has meant that when the company turned over \\u00a33.5m, there were seven people in the warehouse, whereas in 2024 (turnover of \\u00a310m), there are five.Leon Paul has more than 75% of the UK market-including supplying the entire Team GB Olympic fencing team-and recently won the 2024 Kings Award for Enterprise in Innovation and Export, strengthening its recent strategy of focusing mostly on exports.\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 2299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2086, \"end\": 2088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999989204298, \"rank\": 1.0558691865211944e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the business\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"quick and informed decisions\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a33.5m\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"seven people\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1981}, {\"ngram\": \"the warehouse\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"Leon Paul\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 75%\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2078}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire Team GB Olympic fencing team\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2155}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Kings Award\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2193}, {\"ngram\": \"Enterprise\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"Innovation\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2222}, {\"ngram\": \"Export\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2233}, {\"ngram\": \"its recent strategy\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"exports\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To further our global growth plans, we needed a modern warehouse and an ERP system to support our e-commerce engine, ensuring our customers all over the world get the right product in good time,\\\" continued James Fay.\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2372, \"end\": 2382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enterprise_resource_planning\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ERP system\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enterprise_resource_planning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enterprise_resource_planning\"}, {\"begin\": 2506, \"end\": 2515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_H._Fay\", \"score\": 0.9999999998399289, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Fay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_H._Fay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_H._Fay\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our global growth plans\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2334}, {\"ngram\": \"a modern warehouse\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"our e-commerce engine\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"our customers\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2458}, {\"ngram\": \"the right product\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2480}, {\"ngram\": \"good time\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Orderwise has done exactly that and more.\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Orderwise\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly that\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our global agents are also connected to it, and we now all have the information to make smarter, data-based decisions about the business.\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our global agents\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2577}, {\"ngram\": \"the information\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2639}, {\"ngram\": \"smarter, data-based decisions\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2677}, {\"ngram\": \"the business\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Orderwise is an ERP solution that provides wholesalers, distributors, retailers and manufacturers with a platform for growth.\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2714, \"end\": 2717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enterprise_resource_planning\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.502685017658743e-24, \"text\": \"ERP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enterprise_resource_planning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enterprise_resource_planning\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Orderwise\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2707}, {\"ngram\": \"wholesalers\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2752}, {\"ngram\": \"distributors\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2766}, {\"ngram\": \"retailers\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"manufacturers\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"a platform\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2811}, {\"ngram\": \"growth\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was initially deployed by Leon Paul in operational logistics, sales, and customer service, followed by accounts, and is currently being implemented in the manufacturing plant.\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Leon Paul\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"operational logistics\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2887}, {\"ngram\": \"sales\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2894}, {\"ngram\": \"customer service\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2916}, {\"ngram\": \"accounts\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2938}, {\"ngram\": \"the manufacturing plant\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 3001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Leon Paul is an iconic UK manufacturer, rightly celebrated for its quality, longevity and commitment to fencing,\\\" said Jon Roberts, Director, Forterro.\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3026, \"end\": 3028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999989204298, \"rank\": 1.0558691865211944e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3122, \"end\": 3133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jon_Roberts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jon Roberts\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jon_Roberts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jon_Roberts\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Leon Paul\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3012}, {\"ngram\": \"its quality\", \"from\": 3066, \"to\": 3077}, {\"ngram\": \"longevity\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3088}, {\"ngram\": \"commitment\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3103}, {\"ngram\": \"fencing\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3114}, {\"ngram\": \"Director\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"Forterro\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our ERP solutions are all designed with specific industries in mind, and we are very proud that Orderwise has played a role in Leon Paul's success.\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3160, \"end\": 3163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enterprise_resource_planning\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.502685017658743e-24, \"text\": \"ERP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enterprise_resource_planning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enterprise_resource_planning\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"specific industries\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3215}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 3219, \"to\": 3223}, {\"ngram\": \"Orderwise\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3261}, {\"ngram\": \"a role\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3279}, {\"ngram\": \"Leon Paul's success\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"-ends-About Forterro\\u00aeFounded in 2012, Forterro has grown to become a category leader in industrial software - with strongholds in Europe's top production economies, as well as regional service hubs and development centres around the world.\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3543, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Forterro\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3350}, {\"ngram\": \"a category leader\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3388}, {\"ngram\": \"industrial software\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3411}, {\"ngram\": \"strongholds\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3430}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe's top production economies\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3467}, {\"ngram\": \"regional service hubs\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3501}, {\"ngram\": \"development centres\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From more than 40 office locations, its 1,600+ employees provide and support software for more than 13,000 industrial businesses.\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than 40 office locations\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3578}, {\"ngram\": \"its 1,600+ employees\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3600}, {\"ngram\": \"software\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3629}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 13,000 industrial businesses\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 3672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its products are deeply rooted in the demands of their local geography and each is designed to strengthen and accelerate customers' ability to operate efficiently and compete effectively.\\u00a9 Forterro 2024 All rights reservedMedia Contacts:Rise PRPaul AllenEmail:paul@risepr.co.ukPhone: +44 7515 199487ForterroRachel Woodford, PR & CommunicationsEmail:rachel.woodford@forterro.comPhone: +44 7887 791475 This press release was distributed by ResponseSource Press Release Wire on behalf of Rise PR in the following categories:Business & Finance,Retail & Fashion,Manufacturing, Engineering & Energy,Computing & Telecoms, for more information visithttps://pressreleasewire.responsesource.com/about.\", \"from\": 3674, \"to\": 4370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4128, \"end\": 4141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Press_release\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Press Release\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \